            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:norra-rorum"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Virtually all the routes to the right of \"Botten upp\" are more or less covered in moss and obstructed by a large tree that attracts moss, damp, leaves and other debris.",
